com.microsoft.bingads.v13.bulk.entities

Class BulkAdGroupNegativeSites

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.bingads.v13.internal.bulk.BulkObject
      • com.microsoft.bingads.v13.bulk.entities.BulkEntity
        • com.microsoft.bingads.v13.internal.bulk.entities.MultiRecordBulkEntity
          • com.microsoft.bingads.v13.bulk.entities.BulkAdGroupNegativeSites

  • public class BulkAdGroupNegativeSites
extends MultiRecordBulkEntity

    Represents one or more negative sites that are assigned to an ad group. Each negative site can be read or written in a bulk file. This class exposes properties that can be read and written as fields of the Ad Group Negative Site record in a bulk file.

    For more information, see Ad Group Negative Site at https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=846127

    One BulkAdGroupNegativeSites has one or more BulkAdGroupNegativeSite. Each BulkAdGroupNegativeSite instance corresponds to one Ad Group Negative Site record in the bulk file. If you upload a BulkAdGroupNegativeSites, then you are effectively replacing any existing negative sites assigned to the ad group.

    See Also:
    BulkServiceManager, BulkOperation, BulkFileReader, BulkFileWriter
